===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|-}}

# The [[time]] [[ahead]]; those [[moment]]s [[yet]] to be [[experience]]d.
# Something that will happen in moments yet to come.
# Goodness in what is yet to come/Something to look foreward to.
#: ''There is no '''future''' in dwelling on the past.''
# {{grammar}} Verb tense used to talk about events that will happen in the future; [[future tense]].
# {{finance|in the plural}} [[commodities|Commodities]] or [[stocks]] [[bought]] or [[sold]] with the [[understanding]] that they will be delivered at a [[date]] [[beyond]] the [[current]] one.

